text: Lucerne-Land District is a new district of the Swiss canton of Lucerne. These municipalities are in the district: * Adligenswil * Buchrain * Dierikon * Ebikon * Gisikon * Greppen * Honau * Horw * Kriens * Malters * Meggen * Meierskappel * Root * Schwarzenberg * Udligenswil * Vitznau * Weggis Category:2013 establishments in Switzerland
title: Lucerne-Land District
